attributes.action: Stop IR35 roll-out in 2020 in private sector - due to uncertainty around Brexit
attributes.background: The country is already in a state of flux due to the uncertainty around the continued membership of the European Union (Brexit). At this time, it would be economically short sighted of the current Conservative government to make such sweeping changes to a tax legislation.
